currency

Class Money

  • java.lang.Object
    • currency.Money
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Money>

    public final class Money
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<Money>, java.io.Serializable
    Class Money represents an amount of money. It contains a BigDecimal value for the amount, and a CurrencyType constant for the type of currency.
    Version:
    2.0
    Author:
    Craig
